Package: re2-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: re21 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: An efficient regular expression library - development files
 RE2 is a fast, safe, thread-friendly alternative to backtracking
 regular expression engines like those used in PCRE, Perl, and
 Python. It is a C++ library.

Package: re21
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: An efficient regular expression library - shared library
 RE2 is a fast, safe, thread-friendly alternative to backtracking
 regular expression engines like those used in PCRE, Perl, and
 Python. It is a C++ library.
